defaultin the UK 
defaultsuggest that 
defaulthomeopathy can save money 
defaultby reduc
defaulting the 
defaultuse of
default conventional drugs, both in a 
defaulthospital and 
defaulta 
defaultGP setting.
default Specifically,
default a
default 500-patient survey at the Royal London Ho
defaultmeopathic Hospital showed that 
defaultmany patients were able to reduce or stop conventional medication fo
defaultllowing homeopathic treatment (
defaultSharples
default et al., 2003) 
defaultand a
default study examin
defaulting
